flowchart-diagram

title Typing Speed Test Web Application

// Define groups for better organization
User Interaction {
  Open Website [shape: oval, icon: globe]
  Start Test [icon: play-circle]
  Type Text [icon: keyboard]
  Submit Test [icon: send]
  View Results [icon: bar-chart-2]
}

Backend Processes {
  Generate Random Text [icon: file-text]
  Calculate Speed [icon: activity]
  Calculate Accuracy [icon: check-circle]
  Store Results [icon: database]
}

// Define the flow
Open Website > Start Test
Start Test > Generate Random Text
Generate Random Text > Display Text [icon: monitor]
Display Text > Type Text
Type Text > Submit Test
Submit Test > Calculate Speed
Submit Test > Calculate Accuracy
Calculate Speed > Store Results
Calculate Accuracy > Store Results
Store Results > View Results

